## Safety

- `data/session.har` contains live cookies/tokens for `%%HOST%%`. Never print,
  commit to a public repo, or paste its contents. See [SECURITY.md](SECURITY.md).
- State-changing steps (POST/PUT/PATCH/DELETE) require `--confirm-mutating` and
  explicit user approval before replay.
- This skill reuses the session that was recorded; it does not bypass auth. If
  the embedded session expires, re-record with the `teach-web-actions` skill.

